Catalyzes an alkyl-migration followed by a ketol- acid reduction of (S)-2-acetolactate (S2AL) to yield (R)-2,3- dihydroxy-isovalerate. In the isomerase reaction, S2AL is rearranged via a Mg-dependent methyl migration to produce 3- hydroxy-3-methyl-2-ketobutyrate (HMKB).
